Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.69,0:01:49.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Lassie!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.43,0:01:52.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Don't go this way!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.24,0:01:58.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Crossing such river is dangerous to you!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.20,0:02:00.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Lassie!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.53,0:02:06.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Lassie!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.28,0:02:13.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh! Ah!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.42,0:02:17.59,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a dream!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.61,0:02:19.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.86,0:02:21.28,Default,,0,0,0,,It's just a dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.74,0:02:27.11,Default,,0,0,0,,WELCOME BACK, LASSIE
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.32,0:02:33.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}John,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.89,0:02:36.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}There is no news of Lassie for today.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.17,0:02:41.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Its last appearance was\Nthree days ago of West Darlington.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.55,0:02:48.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But I'm sure Lasie has traveled safely and\Nit will arrive soon, that's what I think!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.79,0:02:51.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry, Priscilla!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.94,0:02:56.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Lassie is in good health and is\Non its way to... my house.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.41,0:03:18.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought of Lassie until the morning came...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.89,0:03:35.75,Default,,0,0,0,,It is the result of the geological survey.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.75,0:03:38.66,Default,,0,0,0,,If the result is zero,\NI can't assume that!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.79,0:03:39.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.70,0:03:42.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's do our best and find coal, Dad!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.63,0:03:49.83,Default,,0,0,0,,When I see these two working, I feel\Nthat the coal will definitely come out!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.25,0:03:50.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.17,0:03:54.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, we too will not lose\Nto the current manager!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.33,0:03:55.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.47,0:04:06.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah Sandy!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.34,0:04:08.40,Default,,0,0,0,,How is your health?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.44,0:04:10.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.82,0:04:13.17,Default,,0,0,0,,There is no escape from that as you see...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.37,0:04:15.04,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.16,0:04:16.43,Default,,0,0,0,,This is your gift!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.65,0:04:17.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.40,0:04:19.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.53,0:04:23.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I... why I'm always so?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.44,0:04:26.19,Default,,0,0,0,,And to get sick at such an important time?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.58,0:04:28.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I feel embarrassed by myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.23,0:04:30.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't help John at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.64,0:04:31.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe so!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.71,0:04:33.91,Default,,0,0,0,,So the same with me!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.33,0:04:39.75,Default,,0,0,0,,All I can do is make tea at their own leisure!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.05,0:04:40.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.03,0:04:45.97,Default,,0,0,0,,John is doing hard work like a man.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.28,0:04:46.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah...!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.00,0:04:52.10,Default,,0,0,0,,But when everyone treats the candy they offer\Nthem will increase their strength as I think!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.60,0:04:53.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.77,0:04:55.74,Default,,0,0,0,,John...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.84,0:04:59.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Actually wants to find Lassie but he can't!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.70,0:05:03.75,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why he desperately tries\Nto find coal with others.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.46,0:05:07.99,Default,,0,0,0,,When Lassie returns,\Nthey will always live together.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.43,0:05:10.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.07,0:05:15.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I hope Lassie returns while he is in this area.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.72,0:05:21.46,Default,,0,0,0,,When I see it in good health,\NI expect to stay next to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.90,0:05:22.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.97,0:05:25.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I wish I could do even a little!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.04,0:05:26.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.89,0:05:28.23,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.89,0:05:35.41,Default,,0,0,0,,And now everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.54,0:05:37.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Time for tea!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.36,0:05:39.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh? What is our food today?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.69,0:05:42.31,Default,,0,0,0,,The meat pie is full of energy!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.47,0:05:45.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Every day I look forward to this moment!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.54,0:05:46.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, take a break!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.86,0:05:58.77,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.38,0:06:01.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes! Thank you for the food!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.47,0:06:06.65,Default,,0,0,0,,W-what, did you eat already?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.31,0:06:14.19,Default,,0,0,0,,John!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.48,0:06:15.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.56,0:06:17.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't help much!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.89,0:06:20.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't help too much?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.16,0:06:22.78,Default,,0,0,0,,You do everything you can!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.63,0:06:24.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.69,0:06:26.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What is that?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.67,0:06:29.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, one week only?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.48,0:06:30.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.58,0:06:31.94,Default,,0,0,0,,It is time to hold your breath!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.97,0:06:34.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Wellington Coal Mine has reached its limit.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.55,0:06:38.09,Default,,0,0,0,,The bank is no longer able\Nto pay costs without interest!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.00,0:06:41.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Now we can't extract coal.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.36,0:06:42.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe we should give up.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.99,0:06:45.00,Default,,0,0,0,,But, just a week!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.08,0:06:45.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Sam...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.60,0:06:49.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I have to tell everyone the truth!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.33,0:06:53.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}We need to think about\Nthe future of our new life!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.95,0:06:58.70,Default,,0,0,0,,We should talk to John.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.38,0:07:02.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you have the power to tell him directly?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.38,0:07:05.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not sure I can say it...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.12,0:07:08.13,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I'm going to do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.90,0:07:10.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I think you understand that too...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.92,0:07:14.24,Default,,0,0,0,,John has recently become more mature.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.36,0:07:15.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I wish that he was...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.33,0:07:23.40,Default,,0,0,0,,What is the matter with the manager?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.80,0:07:26.42,Default,,0,0,0,,He seems to be talking\Nabout something different.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.69,0:07:29.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I hope to not say to stop it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.49,0:07:32.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey he's coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.13,0:07:33.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.25,0:07:36.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Listen everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.87,0:07:38.36,Default,,0,0,0,,The manager has something to tell you!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.54,0:07:54.27,Default,,0,0,0,,You see?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.39,0:07:56.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it a unique stone?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.49,0:07:58.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I have extracted it from the wall!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.76,0:07:59.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Sandy!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.01,0:08:01.79,Default,,0,0,0,,This! Probably...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.46,0:08:04.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Just a moment, bring that book to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.41,0:08:05.84,Default,,0,0,0,,- The yellow one!\N- Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.40,0:08:06.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.00,0:08:08.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait for me to sort them out first!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.23,0:08:09.93,Default,,0,0,0,,This one?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.03,0:08:12.93,Default,,0,0,0,,No... that one! The third one!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.07,0:08:14.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Right! That one!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.44,0:08:15.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.33,0:08:17.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm...!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.39,0:08:19.31,Default,,0,0,0,,What is there?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.72,0:08:21.65,Default,,0,0,0,,There it is!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.68,0:08:23.64,Default,,0,0,0,,There it is! Ammonite!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.82,0:08:24.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.93,0:08:25.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Aah!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.66,0:08:26.98,Default,,0,0,0,,This is serious!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.43,0:08:28.41,Default,,0,0,0,,What is the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.43,0:08:30.01,Default,,0,0,0,,That's serious, Sandy!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.15,0:08:30.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.33,0:08:35.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What is the matter?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.97,0:08:39.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Manager, tell us quickly!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.52,0:08:42.17,Default,,0,0,0,,We are also about to lose our temper!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.52,0:08:49.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Manager, should I say that instead of you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.12,0:08:51.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.31,0:08:52.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't say it!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.21,0:08:59.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.58,0:09:00.44,Default,,0,0,0,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.72,0:09:01.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.88,0:09:02.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Somewhat...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.32,0:09:05.71,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.15,0:09:08.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}We have to let you all know...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.42,0:09:10.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Sir!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.28,0:09:13.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey sir! It's serious!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.10,0:09:14.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Serious thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.39,0:09:15.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.01,0:09:19.28,Default,,0,0,0,,What is the matter? Why you were running?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.43,0:09:20.75,Default,,0,0,0,,In fact...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.61,0:09:24.83,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.46,0:09:34.30,Default,,0,0,0,,This...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.33,0:09:35.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh...!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.27,0:09:38.88,Default,,0,0,0,,There it is! It's a carbon\Nelement of antiquity!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.27,0:09:40.54,Default,,0,0,0,,It is an Ammonite...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.19,0:09:42.36,Default,,0,0,0,,This means...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.99,0:09:44.03,Default,,0,0,0,,What does it mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.55,0:09:48.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Coal is a tree grown in the\Nearth since ancient times!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.99,0:09:50.88,Default,,0,0,0,,But this oyster...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.90,0:09:51.91,Default,,0,0,0,,This is not an object!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.01,0:09:55.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah... sir, it is a bit different...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.87,0:09:56.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.67,0:09:59.45,Default,,0,0,0,,In any case, we have to determine
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.47,0:10:01.71,Default,,0,0,0,,the age of this object and it will\Ncertainly determine the age of the tree
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.78,0:10:03.51,Default,,0,0,0,,that has grown since ancient times\Nand is the main source of coal.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.54,0:10:05.84,Default,,0,0,0,,The object indicates\Nthe presence of coal as well...!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.84,0:10:07.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, and charcoal too!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.67,0:10:10.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, we have to dig more!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.93,0:10:14.15,Default,,0,0,0,,We don't know what is coming\Nout to us, but let's dig, let's dig!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.18,0:10:15.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.18,0:10:16.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, Colin!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.64,0:10:18.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, John!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.43,0:10:19.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, Colin!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.95,0:10:20.99,Default,,0,0,0,,No way...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.14,0:10:23.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Sandy is the one who\Npicked it up from the mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.51,0:10:25.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought it was a plain stone.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.10,0:10:27.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Be proud of yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.91,0:10:40.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Hey! Something else appeared!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.36,0:10:41.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it coal?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.54,0:10:43.86,Default,,0,0,0,,No, but it stirred up!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.06,0:10:45.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Traces, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.60,0:10:46.89,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.95,0:10:48.64,Default,,0,0,0,,It looks huge!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.65,0:10:56.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Professor, how was it?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.58,0:10:58.53,Default,,0,0,0,,It's good to find the entire body of Ariophus,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.56,0:11:03.45,Default,,0,0,0,,which is considered one of\Nthe most important ancient relics!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.80,0:11:06.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I heard that the mine will close today!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.97,0:11:09.44,Default,,0,0,0,,After that I can say that coal can go out
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.48,0:11:12.12,Default,,0,0,0,,according to previous geological studies,\Nbut still little possibility.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.12,0:11:16.93,Default,,0,0,0,,And order to close the mine,\Nit's completely wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.95,0:11:21.41,Default,,0,0,0,,So I have to tell the Duke\Nto abandon his decision.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.43,0:11:23.20,Default,,0,0,0,,That's all, sorry I'm going!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.57,0:11:25.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you so much!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.41,0:11:26.23,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.51,0:11:29.19,Default,,0,0,0,,You thank the children!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.22,0:11:29.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.24,0:11:32.20,Default,,0,0,0,,What? What about John?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.35,0:11:35.20,Default,,0,0,0,,He's in the place I found the oyster,\Nand digs with Mr. Pia and the others!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.59,0:11:36.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I'ts enough...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.07,0:11:39.59,Default,,0,0,0,,He wants to continue until the end!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.27,0:11:46.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}John!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.24,0:11:46.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.01,0:11:47.98,Default,,0,0,0,,You have to stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.23,0:11:49.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Leave the rest to your father!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.92,0:11:50.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.75,0:11:52.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}John, come here a little bit!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.88,0:11:54.54,Default,,0,0,0,,What's up, Mr. Pia?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.76,0:11:56.80,Default,,0,0,0,,What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.36,0:12:05.37,Default,,0,0,0,,We have finally done it, John!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.02,0:12:09.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}We did it!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.96,0:12:11.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}We finally did it!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.63,0:12:13.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Coal has come out!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.46,0:12:28.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.06,0:12:45.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Well done, John!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.64,0:12:49.77,Default,,0,0,0,,With this thing Lassie\Ncan come back to me, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.02,0:12:50.74,Default,,0,0,0,,John...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.55,0:12:55.69,Default,,0,0,0,,After feeling comfortable I feel sleepy...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.04,0:12:59.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm glad I trusted you, Dad...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.62,0:13:03.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I... somehow...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.66,0:13:05.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Sleepy...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.71,0:13:07.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Lassie...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.99,0:13:09.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.86,0:13:11.77,Default,,0,0,0,,John...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.09,0:13:22.87,Default,,0,0,0,,He felt relieved after he was nervous!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.65,0:13:28.06,Default,,0,0,0,,So let him sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.23,0:13:30.87,Default,,0,0,0,,What about Lassie?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.21,0:13:35.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I have received a message from\NPriscilla but there is no news of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.45,0:13:36.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.21,0:13:44.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Lassie...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.51,0:13:52.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Wait, Lassie!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.81,0:13:58.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Lassie...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.67,0:14:00.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}So we can always stay together!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.27,0:14:04.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Together...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.98,0:14:08.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Lassie is no longer on my side!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.14,0:14:12.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I wonder if it is still walking?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.46,0:14:16.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But, where does it walk in this world?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.44,0:14:21.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Lassie...!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.70,0:14:25.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Where did you go, Lassie?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.61,0:14:30.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Oh! Where are you now?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.43,0:14:33.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Where do you walk now?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.80,0:14:43.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Lassie!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.13,0:14:54.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Lassie!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.64,0:15:01.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Lassie... I'm sorry...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.32,0:15:04.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I've made you tire a lot!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.62,0:15:11.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}John?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.06,0:15:13.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.05,0:15:17.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.59,0:15:21.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Priscilla?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.65,0:15:25.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you sleep well?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.67,0:15:29.20,Default,,0,0,0,,They came from Scotland by plane.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.97,0:15:31.52,Default,,0,0,0,,By plane!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.81,0:15:33.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Did I sleep?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.72,0:15:34.89,Default,,0,0,0,,For two days!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.19,0:15:35.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.44,0:15:38.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Have I really slept all this time?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.09,0:15:40.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}John!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.93,0:15:43.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Congratulations!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.24,0:15:44.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Because of your faith,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.70,0:15:48.99,Default,,0,0,0,,you brought the coal out again,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.11,0:15:50.45,Default,,0,0,0,,though I didn't believe it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.55,0:15:51.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.65,0:15:53.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}You've done a really good job!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.37,0:15:56.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Your heart has won over me!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.15,0:15:58.10,Default,,0,0,0,,However...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.55,0:16:00.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I apologise...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.33,0:16:05.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I promised you that I would give Lassie back.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.11,0:16:07.41,Default,,0,0,0,,But I couldn't keep it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.74,0:16:10.33,Default,,0,0,0,,You are the only one who\Ncan take care of Lassie!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.36,0:16:11.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Right, Lassie!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.01,0:16:13.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I have to find Lassie!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.44,0:16:18.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Lassie is still walking towards our village!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.26,0:16:18.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.15,0:16:21.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Get out! My clothes!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.36,0:16:23.36,Default,,0,0,0,,- John!\N- You'll change your clothes, John?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.96,0:16:26.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Listen, John
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.82,0:16:30.66,Default,,0,0,0,,If Lassie returns,\Nit will be like a miracle!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.66,0:16:31.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Grandfather!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.74,0:16:32.20,Default,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.59,0:16:35.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I apologize but I don't know what to say!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.34,0:16:37.92,Default,,0,0,0,,No, Lassie is still walking to here!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.94,0:16:38.85,Default,,0,0,0,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.01,0:16:40.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I saw that!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.10,0:16:41.28,Default,,0,0,0,,That Lassie is coming here!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.46,0:16:42.40,Default,,0,0,0,,You have seen?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.40,0:16:44.39,Default,,0,0,0,,But, where are you going?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.51,0:16:45.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't it clear?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.56,0:16:46.67,Default,,0,0,0,,To the north side!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.69,0:16:49.81,Default,,0,0,0,,When Lassie left Scotland\Nit walked straight toward this village!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.24,0:17:05.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey John!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.71,0:17:06.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Where are you going?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.79,0:17:07.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Lassie!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.01,0:17:08.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.76,0:17:11.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Lassie is on its way back here!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.78,0:17:13.57,Default,,0,0,0,,It will arrive here soon!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.59,0:17:14.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.24,0:17:23.20,Default,,0,0,0,,To north, to north!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.65,0:17:24.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}To north!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.20,0:17:28.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}This is the right direction!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.54,0:17:31.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}If I turn here I will meet Lassie!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.27,0:18:08.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.10,0:18:11.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Lassie!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.51,0:18:25.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.43,0:18:32.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Lassie!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.81,0:18:34.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Lassie!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.29,0:18:47.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Lassie!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.11,0:18:59.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Lassie!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.32,0:19:11.81,Default,,0,0,0,,No way, Lassie!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.73,0:19:19.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Lassie!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.48,0:19:22.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.44,0:19:42.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Lassie...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.54,0:20:08.23,Default,,0,0,0,,This way! John turned this way!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.07,0:20:10.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.67,0:20:11.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.37,0:20:16.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you okay, Lassie?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.05,0:20:19.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you walk to get home?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.82,0:20:33.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.23,0:20:34.40,Default,,0,0,0,,John
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.48,0:20:35.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Lassie!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.71,0:20:36.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Lassie!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.78,0:20:40.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Lassie!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.18,0:20:42.45,Default,,0,0,0,,- Lassie...\N- Welcome back, Lassie!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.82,0:21:17.67,Default,,0,0,0,,The Wellington Coal Mine is back in business!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.69,0:21:18.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.47,0:21:19.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.22,0:21:20.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Look there!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.90,0:21:27.59,Default,,0,0,0,,John! Lassie!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.61,0:21:29.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Father! Mom!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.18,0:21:32.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Look, everyone came for you, Lassie!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.49,0:21:41.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.79,0:21:42.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.96,0:21:44.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.49,0:22:02.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}After a long journey,\NLassie returned to our village!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.65,0:22:06.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}After that it became famous in the newspapers!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.63,0:22:10.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That's why Duke Rudering decided\Nto organize a big party for it!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.76,0:22:14.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The last episode:\NRUNNING TOWARDS THE DREAM{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.85,0:22:16.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Be sure to watch!{\i0}
